#Ask the user to enter a number 1, 2 or 3
#If the enter a 1, display the message “thank you”
#If they enter a 2, display “well done, you're so smart”
#If they enter a 3, display “amazing, you are so good at this”
#If they enter anything else, display “really? What is wrong with you??”

num = int(input("Enter a number: "))

if num == 1:
    print("Thank you")
elif num == 2:
    print("Well done, you're so smart")
elif num == 3:
    print("Amazing, you're so good at this!")
else: 
    print("Really? What is wrong with you?")
